data.description: LISTED BELOW MARKET VALUE!! INSTANT EQUITY!!   VA ASSUMABLE LOAN 3.25%***** MOTIVATED SELLER! BRING YOUR OFFER!    Beautifully and totally remodeled open concept spacious home with 3 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms. Generously sized Primary bedroom, a gorgeous ensuite bathroom with a large tub and a large walk-in closet and a sliding glass door that leads out to the backyard. The 2 other well-appointed bedrooms are on the opposite side of the home from the primary bedroom. The kitchen is completely open with a large bar with stainless steel kitchen appliances. Home also has an attached 2 car garage and 4 tandem parking spots. Conveniently located near Schofield Barracks, Wheeler Army base, Dole Plantation and the world-famous North Shore. 18 miles to the airport and 20 miles to Honolulu. You don't want to miss this one! Bring your buyers!
